title: What It Takes to Really Change - Part 1
description: For change to happen in any area of your life — whether it’s financial, vocational, educational, mental, or relational —begin with the physical. In this broadcast, Pastor Rick teaches what the apostle Paul meant when he said “offer your bodies as a living sacrifice, holy and pleasing to God” (Romans 12:1).
